<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>CenterED Coaching</title>
  
  
  <style>
/* General styling */
body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  background-color: #f4f4f4;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

a {
  text-decoration: none;
  color: #333;
}

button {
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border: none;
  background-color: #007BFF;
  color: #fff;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  border-radius: 5px; /* Add border radius */
}

button:hover {
  background-color: #0056b3;
}

/* Header styling */
.header {
  background-color: #3498db;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 20px 0;
}

.navigation {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-around;
}

.logo {
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: bold;
  color: #fff;
}

.navigation a {
  color: #fff;
}
.navigation a:hover {
      color: violet;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
.hero {
  background-image: url("/assets/hugs.jpeg");
  text-align: center;
  padding: 40px 0;
}

/* Dropdown Button */
.dropbtn {
  background-color: #007BFF;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px;
  font-size: 16px;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
}

/* The container <div> - needed to position the dropdown content */
.dropdown {
  position: relative;
  display: inline-block;
}

/* Dropdown Content (Hidden by Default) */
.dropdown-content {
  display: none
  position: absolute;
  background-color: #f9f9f9;
  min-width: 160px;
  box-shadow: 0px 8px 16px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  z-index: 1;
}

/* Links inside the dropdown */
.dropdown-content a {
  color: black;
  padding: 12px 16px;
  text-decoration: none;
  display: block;
}

/* Change color of dropdown links on hover */
.dropdown-content a:hover {background-color: #f1f1f1}

/* Show the dropdown menu on hover */
.dropdown:hover .dropdown-content {display: block;}

/* Change the background color of the dropdown button when the dropdown content is shown */
.dropdown:hover .dropbtn {background-color: #3e8e41;}

/* Actions container */
.actions {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  flex-direction: column;
  width: 50%; /* adjust as needed */
  margin: 0 auto; /* centers the container on the page */
}

/* Goal, category, and button container */
.goal-category-container {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  width: 100%; /* takes up the full width of the .actions container */
}

/* Input field styling */
input[type="text"] {
  flex: 1; /* takes up 1/3 of the container width */
  padding: 10px;
  margin-right: 10px;
  border: 1px solid #ccc;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

/* Dropdown select styling */
select {
  flex: 1; /* takes up 1/3 of the container width */
  padding: 10px;
  border: 1px solid #ccc;
  border-radius: 4px;
  background-color: #f8f8f8;
  cursor: pointer;
}

/* Find a coach button styling */
button {
  flex: 1; /* takes up 1/3 of the container width */
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border: none;
  background-color: #007BFF;
  color: #fff;
  cursor: pointer;
}

/* Main content styling */
.main-content {
  text-align:center;
  padding: 40px 10%;
}

.guidance {
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  text-align:center;
}

.card-container {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  margin-top:20px;
}
.card {
  background-color: #fff;
  width: 100%;
  height:auto; 
  padding: 20px;
  margin: 20px;
  flex: 0 1 calc(25% - 40px); /* Adjust flex */
}

/* Footer styling */
.footer {
  background-color: #3498db;
  color: #fff;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px 0;
}

.getStarted{
  background-color: #3498db;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center; /* centers the contents vertically */
  justify-content: center; /* centers the contents horizontally */
  padding: 20px; /* adds some space around the contents */
  margin-top: 40px;
}
.getStarted h2{
  color: #fff;
}
.getStarted .content{
  color: #fff;
}
/* Card container */
.card-container {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 20px;
}

/* Card styling */
.card {
  flex: 1 0 20%; /* grow, shrink, basis */
  padding: 16px;
  text-align: center;
  background-color: #F2FDFF;
  margin: 10px;
  border-radius:5px;
}

/* Responsive styling */
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .card-container {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .card {
    width: 100%;
  }
}

  </style>


</head>
<body>
  <header class="header">
    <div class="navigation">
      <a href="/" class="logo">Center<span style="color:violet;">ED</span></a>
      <a href="/">About</a>
      <a href="/student/login">Student Login</a>
      <a href="/admin/login">Admin</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Prepare for Your Future with Career Coaching with CenterED</h1>
        <p>Get the guidance and support you need to achieve your career goals.</p>
        
        <div class="actions">
          <div class="goal-category-container">
            <input type="text" id="goal" name="goal" placeholder="Set your goal">
            <div class="dropdown">
              <select id="category" name="category">
                <option value="">Set a category</option>
                <option value="career-advice">Career Advice</option>
                <option value="resume-review">Resume Review</option>
                <option value="mock-interview">Mock Interview</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href = "/student/login"><button>Find a coach</button></a>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="main-content">
    <section class="guidance">
      <h2>Get the Guidance and Support You Need</h2>
      <p>Whether you're just starting out or you're looking to make a career change, we can help you to put your best foot forward and achieve your career goals.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="card-container">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Career Advice</h3>
        <p>We offer personalized career advice to help you identify your career goals, develop a plan to achieve them, and build your skills and knowledge.</p>
        <a href="/student/login"><button>Get started</button></a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Resume Review</h3>
        <p>We offer expert resume reviews to help you write a resume, tailored to your specific career goals and that will stand out to recruiters and hiring managers.</p>
        <a href="/student/login"><button>Get started</button></a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Mock Interview</h3>
        <p>We offer one-on-one mock interviews to help you prepare for and ace your next job interview.</p>
        <a href="/student/login"><button>Get started</button></a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

    <div class="getStarted">
  <h2>How to get started</h2>
  <p class="content">Ready to take the next step in your career? Follow these simple steps to get started with us</p>
  <div class="card-container">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Tell us about yourself and your goals</h3>
      <p>What are your career goals? What are your strengths and weaknesses? What are your budget, experience, and desired outcome? The more information you can provide, the better we can match you with the best-fit coach.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Browse coaches and set up free intro calls</h3>
      <p>Once you've created your profile, you can browse our directory of coaches and set up free intro calls. This is a great opportunity to learn more about each coach's approach and see if they're a good fit for you.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Get started with your coach</h3>
      <p>Once you've found a coach you like, you can book your first session. Your coach will work with you to develop a personalized coaching plan and help you achieve your goals.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Attend a group class</h3>
      <p>In addition to one-on-one coaching, we also offer a variety of group classes on relevant career and education topics. These classes are a great way to learn from top coaches and connect with other professionals who are on similar journeys.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

